1.	I125 Reverse T3, 13 mL. contains RT3 labeled with I125 in Tris buffer with sodium azide.
2.	RT3 Calibrators: CAL 1~7: 1 mL each; CAL 0:2 mL.

5.	20% TW PEG Solution: 125 mL.
